{"tid":675330,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好唔信邪! 小米將跳過「7」直接推出小米8旗艦新機","createTime":"2018-05-23T12:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T09:36:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"af36a1e5a8e22688af2fe0ab95f824e4313fb8de","tid":675330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"Blackie Digital<br />\n<br />\n命名有時真是「唔好唔信邪」，就好像Samsung當年推出Galaxy Note 7連番出事，未知國內廠商小米是否汲取了相關教訓，準備跳過小米7的命名，直接推出小米8旗艦新機。而從日前流出的新機介紹投影片中，除了可以看到小米8的名字，更有新機的主要規格曝光，包括6.01吋屏幕、Snapdragon 845處理器、AI相機等。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.android-hk.com/news/xiaomi_mi_8_cost_400_leaked_pricing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fnews%2Fxiaomi_mi_8_cost_400_leaked_pricing%2F&d=vpYrFJbs0IQmUCDlfh9O0NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=5262baa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.android-hk.com/news/xiaomi_mi_8_cost_400_leaked_pricing/</a>"},{"pid":"b0245fd5c270b776f9b1d8f7aec290cd1780896f","tid":675330,"uid":87339,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"小米， 就是柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cec7fc90478255271980c932302bf5d69bbc8a","tid":675330,"uid":174418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:20:28.000Z","msg":"有錢賺就得 出7 可能賺唔到錢"},{"pid":"e393d7b17d4a394d1ae91b000f70ed625a32fafb","tid":675330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T20:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381e54631e592a4cb87583aee2e8a6ea9555f275","tid":675330,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T23:46:08.000Z","msg":"無柒用"},{"pid":"10441f8990d2b929252aa4eac05ce568d2485e29","tid":675330,"uid":155374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:12:11.000Z","msg":"點解雜種你啲料咁舊嘅，一早出到小米9啦<br />\n<br />\n各大forum都好多小米狗<i